=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &amp;gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  &amp;gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &amp;gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n公司爆屎渠 幫手拖屎水"},{"pid":"1acc9474e4eb06b861aa81c7fd754366cf527982","tid":86224,"uid":1189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T08:27:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做過碼頭吊機手去夾櫃個車頭佬個櫃唔記得甩lock。個陣同人講緊電話。吊起左佢成個櫃咁高。嚇到瀨屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嘩屌 個車頭佬係半空應該嚇到暈左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正常情況個車頭佬係會跳車。佢唔跳仲係到響安先on9.,好彩之後發現慢慢放番低佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌你，咩野叫正常情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc95441a63e44f5a8b91aaeccee39ff0100fb528","tid":86224,"uid":71441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T08:34:02.000Z","msg":"早過老細走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8b474d9220139fae6d8bdfe9a151140c0226fe6","tid":86224,"uid":25224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T08:34:43.000Z","msg":"喺街跌左3萬蚊貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"164519b9d7c46e641299fc2ac4aa0860d59865c9","tid":86224,"uid":12653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T08:37:18.000Z","msg":"訓教俾客見到<br />\n當場問我叫咩名投訴<br />\n第二日照常番工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f239a1a8837647bf88577600e05ef4bebaf3b18","tid":86224,"uid":104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T08: